      <title>黄金价格高企 中国黄金进口量下降近三分之二</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/chinese-gold-imports-fell-by-almost-two-thirds-on-high-prices</link>
      <description><![CDATA[上个月，中国的黄金进口量大幅下降，表明在经济低迷的情况下，中国买家因贵金属价格上涨而望而却步。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/chinese-gold-imports-fell-by-almost-two-thirds-on-high-prices</guid>
